WaveCrux C ABI header
---------------------
The shim crate vendors a copy of `wavecrux_decoder.h` from the WaveCrux
open-core repository (`wavecrux/include/wavecrux_decoder.h`). That header
will become Apache-2.0 when the WaveCrux open-core repository transitions
out of public beta; until then it is shipped under WaveCrux's pre-release
license. Either license is compatible with this repo's GPLv3+ for the
purpose of providing the C ABI binding contract.


